nodes.text: Janina Zione Gavankar (born November 29, 1980) is an American actress who portrayed Iden Versio in Star Wars Battlefront II. Gavankar  also read the audiobook for the 2017 novel Battlefront II: Inferno Squad. as well as the short story "End of Watch" for the audiobook of the anthology From a Certain Point of View. She later provided additional voice work for the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker.
Gavankar is known for playing the shapeshifter Luna Garza on HBO's True Blood, McKenna Hall on The CW's Arrow, and Special Agent Diana Thomas on the FOX supernatural drama Sleepy Hollow.
